This product includes software developed at:
[Autoscaler tool for Cloud Spanner](https://github.com/cloudspannerecosystem/autoscaler/tree/main) Copyright Google

The modifications include:
- Scaler: modify to pull metrics from CloudSQL instead of Spanner
- Poller: new scalling method based on available tier (machine types) for CloudSQL Enterprise Plus
- Terraform: simplified and removed the provisioned test instance and state management outside of Firestore

